      "date": "2013-03-06 21:22:41.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: Fails\n\nTests received by maloo, run on el6/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/ebda3118-86a3-11e2-84bd-52540035b04c).  Ran 2 tests.  1 tests failed: lustre-initialization-1.",
