          "date": "2013-03-06 11:32:11.000000000",
          "tz": 0
        },
        "subject": "LU-398 nrs: Do not include NRS in client-only builds",
        "message": "LU-398 nrs: Do not include NRS in client-only builds\n\nDo not include NRS in client only builds, and also include only a\nminimal feature set for liblustre, i.e. the framework and the FIFO\npolicy, as since liblustre is single-threaded, it does not make much\nsense for it to make use of more elaborate policies.\n\nSigned-off-by: Nikitas Angelinas <nikitas_angelinas@xyratex.com>\nChange-Id: I1de0b2f854d066cd395d0154278039632e296642\nOracle-bug-id: b=13634\nXyratex-bug-id: MRP-73\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
